item.title: Introductions are in Order
item.description: Introduction Link to heading Hello and welcome to my blog! For my blog, I will be writing about my journey both as a Software Engineer but also as a person. I hope you enjoy the content I put out and I hope you learn something from it! More About Me Link to heading I was born in the 90’s, a time when computers were just beginning to enter the mainstream.
